{"tid":457372,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點撚解新買木砧板都可以咁撚臭!?","createTime":"2017-11-03T20:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T13:39:58.000Z","uid":52056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"62e9ced2d0fd23c4f7bf3b70ff6ba6abd95bbff0","tid":457372,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T20:13:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 今日老母喺街邊家具店買咗塊木砧板, 傳統中式一大嚿木嗰隻<br />\n一打開個包裝就成陣類似腳臭嘅味湧出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n包裝寫木砧板有味好正常, 要浸一日鹽水再抹油辟味<br />\n於是老母放咗個砧板落鋅盤浸, 一路浸陣味一路散出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發夢都估唔到一嚿木竟然可以臭過公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家浸咗成晚個廚房同客廳彌漫住強勁嘅腳臭, 臭撚到瞓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a5613f29ae285f9752d39bea9e73b77dbc467c","tid":457372,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T20:29:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.gohome.com.hk/tc/living-info/新買砧板發臭-如何辟味？/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gohome.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fliving-info%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%B2%B7%E7%A0%A7%E6%9D%BF%E7%99%BC%E8%87%AD-%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%BE%9F%E5%91%B3%EF%BC%9F%2F&d=9OMDtgqKsXJWl5qPXZvpZ0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=1c28875b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.gohome.com.hk/tc/living-info/新買砧板發臭-如何辟味？/</a><br />\n呢度話浸濃鹽水兩三日"},{"pid":"96cadfaed4ed39a7928a579e965d645aa485a9d3","tid":457372,"uid":73454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T20:47:47.000Z","msg":"掉左佢，買塊靚既竹砧板啦"},{"pid":"9e2bd6aa2ca559a15eadc9a8ab265c2723d69492","tid":457372,"uid":27305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T21:49:45.000Z","msg":"個啲棺木黎"},{"pid":"83cf3e5280ca8071a6427fcb89c594aea38785fa","tid":457372,"uid":740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T22:50:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個啲棺木黎</blockquote><br />\n棺木香㗎"},{"pid":"cdbe988f7908f0a3b6dccd6a074071f789737e54"